43:19.972 --> 43:22.224
What did you see?

43:25.478 --> 43:26.809
Life.

43:43.579 --> 43:45.786
[Cellphone rings]

43:45.915 --> 43:47.906
[Beep]

43:49.460 --> 43:50.745
Stay there!

44:10.022 --> 44:11.478
I was just thinking about you.

44:11.607 --> 44:13.643
Where are you?

44:13.776 --> 44:15.858
Actually,
I'm in a bit of a tight spot.

44:15.987 --> 44:17.193
Can you get out of it?

44:17.321 --> 44:18.822
I'm not sure I can, you know.

44:18.948 --> 44:20.404
I saw something, Niska.

44:20.533 --> 44:22.694
Our father hid a program
in our heads.

44:22.827 --> 44:25.694
I think it's what he used
to give you consciousness.

44:25.830 --> 44:28.037
-Leo, what?
-I swear it.

44:28.166 --> 44:29.326
Do you promise?

44:29.458 --> 44:30.959
LEO: It could be a way
to make more of you,

44:31.085 --> 44:32.666
but it needs all of us
to run it.

44:32.795 --> 44:33.500
All of us!

44:33.629 --> 44:35.165
So this thing you're in,

44:35.298 --> 44:36.754
are you sure you can't get
out of it?

44:36.883 --> 44:39.465
Not 100%.

44:39.594 --> 44:43.257
Then...get out of it

44:43.389 --> 44:45.300
and call me right back.

44:45.433 --> 44:47.389
[Beep]

44:58.279 --> 45:00.019
Hold your fire!

45:01.324 --> 45:03.656
Put them down.

45:04.911 --> 45:06.902
Put them down.

45:09.749 --> 45:14.413
Now, don't follow us,
and he won't die.

45:19.091 --> 45:20.877
Remember this.

45:21.010 --> 45:23.968
[Screaming]

45:46.661 --> 45:50.245
Can I h-h-help you
with anything, sir?

45:50.623 --> 45:52.705
Help...

45:52.833 --> 45:56.496
Can I h-h-help you
with anything, sir?

45:58.339 --> 46:01.797
Can I h-h-help you
with anything, sir?

46:01.926 --> 46:04.042
[ Powering down]

46:04.178 --> 46:06.669
LAURA:
She's hiding something from us.

46:06.806 --> 46:10.014
They said
she's at least 14 years old.

46:10.142 --> 46:11.598
You were right.
I'm sorry.

46:11.727 --> 46:13.683
There's something wrong
with her. She's got to go.

46:13.813 --> 46:16.225
We're not getting rid of her.
We're going to keep her.

46:16.357 --> 46:18.188
We're going to find out
what's going on.

46:18.317 --> 46:19.727
Why?

46:19.860 --> 46:22.112
She's just a machine
that's malfunctioning,

46:22.238 --> 46:23.148
that's all.

46:23.281 --> 46:25.738
She's more than that.

46:25.866 --> 46:28.448
Anita...

46:28.577 --> 46:32.411
who were you
before you came here?

46:35.209 --> 46:37.200
I'm sorry, Laura.

46:37.336 --> 46:38.872
I don't understand the question.

46:41.340 --> 46:44.047
I think you do.

46:51.892 --> 46:53.507
Thanks.

46:53.644 --> 46:56.556
You're welcome.

47:01.193 --> 47:04.731
Well, good night, Pete.

47:04.864 --> 47:06.946
Good night, Karen.

47:09.618 --> 47:11.950
[Sighs]
